Package: charite
Type: Package
Title: A ggplot2 theme and plotting tools for the Charité corporate identity
Version: 0.4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Author: Johannes Julius Mohn
Maintainer: Johannes Julius Mohn <johannes.mohn@charite.de>
Description: A minimal R package which provides a ggplot2 theme and color definitions following the Charité corporate identity style guide. When using the package, please acknowledge the author.
